title: The Complete Capitol Recordings Of Woody Herman (1948-56)
description:
THE COMPLETE CAPITOL RECORDINGS OF WOODY HERMAN

Six CD set with small booklet scans.

Covers 1948-1956. Session info on scans.

Includes Red Rodney, Ernie Royal, Shorty Rogers, Bill Harris, All Cohn, Zoot Sims, Richie Kamuca, Serge Chaloff, Terry Gibbs, Chubby Jackson, Mary Ann McCall, Oscar Pettiford, Shelly Manne, Gene Ammons, Jimmy Giuffre, Lou Levy, Ralph Burns, Clyde Hurley, Eddie Miller, Milt Jackson, Conte Candoli, Neal Hefti, Dave McKenna, Red Mitchell, Bill Perkins, Dick Hafer, Al Porcino, Bernie Glow, and many others, plus two tracks with The Nat King Cole Trio.

2000 Mosaic Records
